140
00:11:25,325 --> 00:11:29,093
[SPEAKER_24]: No, we are absolutely trying to win, believe me.

141
00:11:29,514 --> 00:11:38,693
[SPEAKER_24]: And I think the other thing that Grant was pointing out was that a vote for anybody other than the Conservative Party will allow Keir Starmer into 10 Downing Street.

142
00:11:38,713 --> 00:11:40,617
[SPEAKER_24]: And we know that that comes with

143
00:11:40,934 --> 00:11:45,540
