488
00:37:34,954 --> 00:37:36,797
[SPEAKER_31]: But the other thing I'd say, Beth, because I do think this is important.

489
00:37:36,817 --> 00:37:38,280
[SPEAKER_31]: But do you think they're wrong in principle?

490
00:37:38,340 --> 00:37:40,204
