[SPEAKER_31]: energy nationalisation, which a lot of people think we should nationalise our energy companies.

492
00:37:45,072 --> 00:37:48,298
[SPEAKER_31]: They're making a huge amount of money, lots of people are paying a fortune on their bills.

493
00:37:48,378 --> 00:38:00,118
