496
00:38:15,065 --> 00:38:16,987
[SPEAKER_31]: I thought that would have been the wrong decision.

497
00:38:17,048 --> 00:38:29,904
[SPEAKER_31]: I think most people watching this here or on the television would say, for heaven's sake here, if it's a choice between keeping my bills low or paying off shareholders tens of billions of pounds, there's only one choice you can make.

498
00:38:30,105 --> 00:38:33,108
[SPEAKER_31]: And that's what I mean by country first, party second.

499
00:38:33,148 --> 00:38:34,150
[SPEAKER_31]: I changed my mind.

500
00:38:34,390 --> 00:38:35,191
