517
00:39:31,542 --> 00:39:33,244
[SPEAKER_31]: Swerve the top 5% of earners there.

518
00:39:33,264 --> 00:39:33,984
[SPEAKER_31]: No, no, no.

519
00:39:34,004 --> 00:39:35,446
[SPEAKER_31]: Nothing requires us to raise tax.

520
00:39:35,466 --> 00:39:38,989
[SPEAKER_31]: And I tell you... OK. No, no, I do want to... You'll challenge me and I want to deal with this.

521
00:39:39,369 --> 00:39:40,911
