522
00:39:40,931 --> 00:39:42,452
[SPEAKER_31]: I want to grow our economy.

523
00:39:42,472 --> 00:39:42,713
[SPEAKER_31]: OK.

524
00:39:42,773 --> 00:39:49,099
[SPEAKER_31]: I accept that previous Labour leaders have sort of pulled the tax lever every single time and driven up spending.

