1565
01:50:03,001 --> 01:50:08,588
[SPEAKER_44]: And what are your plans to improve relations and build trust between the police and our communities?

1566
01:50:14,643 --> 01:50:25,125
[SPEAKER_27]: Well, misogyny, racism, discrimination has absolutely no place in our society, but particularly when it comes to the police, because they're people that we look to to protect us and trust.

1567
01:50:25,145 --> 01:50:35,065
[SPEAKER_27]: And all the things that we've seen and read about over the past year or two have been really appalling and shocked us to a core, because we thought, hang on, the people that we put our trust in

