03:23:23,440 --> 03:23:26,626
[SPEAKER_48]: Brighton Pavilion is the only seat the Greens currently hold.

2831
03:23:27,047 --> 03:23:29,431
[SPEAKER_48]: They have a near 20,000 majority.

2832
03:23:29,912 --> 03:23:32,176
[SPEAKER_48]: But voters here aren't all convinced.

