2835
03:23:36,504 --> 03:23:39,209
[SPEAKER_41]: I do like what they're trying to do, I must admit.

2836
03:23:39,510 --> 03:23:41,373
[SPEAKER_41]: So yeah, I'm all for what they do.

2837
03:23:42,035 --> 03:23:46,022
