[SPEAKER_48]: Garepreet Narwan, Sky News, Brighton.

2841
03:24:05,352 --> 03:24:11,841
[SPEAKER_46]: Well, let's just take you through a list now of all the candidates standing in the Brighton Pavilion seat.

2842
03:24:18,908 --> 03:24:27,740
[SPEAKER_46]: In other news, the United States Secretary of State Antony Blinken has said that some of Hamas's demands to change the ceasefire deal are unworkable.

2843
03:24:28,481 --> 03:24:31,825
[SPEAKER_46]: That's after Hamas said it wants written guarantees from the US.

2844
03:24:32,446 --> 03:24:41,338
[SPEAKER_46]: The UN voted in favour of the framework devised by President Biden this week, just days after four hostages were rescued from Gaza.

2845
03:24:41,318 --> 03:24:44,983
[SPEAKER_46]: Sky News has been speaking to the parents of one of the freed hostages.

2846
03:24:45,524 --> 03:24:49,950
[SPEAKER_46]: His rescue was filmed in dramatic footage released by Israeli forces.

2847
03:24:50,571 --> 03:24:53,195
[SPEAKER_46]: Sky's Middle East correspondent Alistair Bunkle reports.

2848
03:24:55,619 --> 03:25:11,241
[SPEAKER_05]: After eight months of hoping that he was still alive, but hearing nothing about his condition or whereabouts, Andrei Kozlov's parents simply couldn't believe it when they got the call to say he'd been rescued and was on a helicopter out of Gaza.

2849
03:25:11,356 --> 03:25:12,958
[SPEAKER_61]: When I heard, are you sitting down?

2850
03:25:12,978 --> 03:25:14,581
[SPEAKER_61]: I thought it was bad news.

2851
03:25:14,601 --> 03:25:16,644
[SPEAKER_61]: I dropped the phone to one side.

2852
03:25:17,225 --> 03:25:18,326
[SPEAKER_61]: It fell under the table.

2853
03:25:18,727 --> 03:25:22,592
[SPEAKER_61]: And suddenly I heard from under the table, it's good news, it's good news.

2854
03:25:22,652 --> 03:25:24,635
[SPEAKER_61]: And I crawled under the table.

2855
03:25:24,655 --> 03:25:25,637
[SPEAKER_61]: Did you see good news?

2856
03:25:26,278 --> 03:25:28,982
[SPEAKER_61]: Yes, they're bringing Andrei over by helicopter.

2857
03:25:29,082 --> 03:25:32,467
[SPEAKER_61]: He's almost in Israel.

2858
03:25:33,368 --> 03:25:37,153
[SPEAKER_14]: It was very emotional.

2859
03:25:37,454 --> 03:25:38,916
[SPEAKER_14]: It's difficult to describe.

2860
03:25:43,402 --> 03:25:51,361
[SPEAKER_05]: Evgenia and Mikhail flew straight from St Petersburg in Russia for an emotional reunion with Ondrej at a hospital in Israel.

2861
03:25:52,965 --> 03:25:57,917
[SPEAKER_05]: It appeared to be the moment his ordeal finally caught up with him.

2862
03:25:59,095 --> 03:26:07,307
[SPEAKER_61]: During the eight months we'd been waiting for him, we feared he would be changed a lot, that he would be a different man.

2863
03:26:07,327 --> 03:26:14,978
[SPEAKER_61]: And suddenly there was this emotional shock.

2864
03:26:15,459 --> 03:26:17,161
[SPEAKER_61]: Mama, mama, I knew I'd return.

2865
03:26:17,241 --> 03:26:20,366
[SPEAKER_61]: Mama, I knew on October 7th that I would go home.

2866
03:26:20,786 --> 03:26:25,373
[SPEAKER_61]: When he calmed down and was able to speak calmly, I knew he was the same man.

2867
03:26:27,428 --> 03:26:37,338
[SPEAKER_05]: Andrei was rescued with two Israeli men, Almogmer Jan and Shlomi Zev, in an Israeli military operation in central Gaza on Saturday morning.

2868
03:26:42,844 --> 03:26:46,788
[SPEAKER_05]: What has he told you about the last eight months?

2869
03:26:47,809 --> 03:26:56,878
[SPEAKER_61]: One of the phrases that really scared or hurt us was when he said, there are some things I will never tell you about.

2870
03:26:57,533 --> 03:26:59,516
[SPEAKER_61]: As for everything else, yes, he tells us.

2871
03:27:00,037 --> 03:27:03,963
[SPEAKER_61]: But it's as if he's playing storyteller, as if to entertain us.

2872
03:27:04,564 --> 03:27:09,912
[SPEAKER_61]: Even the fact that his hands and feet were tied for two months, he tells it as if it were a joke.

2873
03:27:13,498 --> 03:27:19,608
[SPEAKER_05]: Hamas claims that at least 270 Gazans were killed and hundreds wounded in the rescue operation.

2874
03:27:20,830 --> 03:27:25,617
[SPEAKER_05]: Video from the scene shows many dead in the densely populated Muzurat market.

2875
03:27:27,503 --> 03:27:32,608
[SPEAKER_05]: Hamas now says it wants written guarantees from the US before agreeing a ceasefire deal.

2876
03:27:33,209 --> 03:27:38,914
[SPEAKER_05]: But the US Secretary of State in Qatar today said some of Hamas's demands aren't possible.

2877
03:27:39,955 --> 03:27:45,541
[SPEAKER_00]: Hamas has proposed numerous changes to the proposal that was on the table.

2878
03:27:45,561 --> 03:27:48,364
[SPEAKER_00]: Some of the changes are workable, some are not.

2879
03:27:50,185 --> 03:27:52,768
[SPEAKER_00]: Here, in a nutshell, is where we stand.

2880
03:27:53,440 --> 03:28:00,455
[SPEAKER_05]: For all the hostages who have returned home, like Andrei, 120 still remain in Gaza, many of them dead.

2881
03:28:01,156 --> 03:28:07,069
[SPEAKER_05]: Negotiations for their release continue, but hopes for a ceasefire are again fading.

2882
03:28:07,891 --> 03:28:10,015
[SPEAKER_05]: Alistair Bunkle, Sky News, in Tel Aviv.

2883
03:28:12,762 --> 03:28:20,594
[SPEAKER_46]: Jurors in the retrial of Lucy Letby have been told her previous conviction should be taken into account as an important piece of evidence.

2884
03:28:21,375 --> 03:28:32,713
[SPEAKER_46]: The former nurse is accused of the attempted murder of a baby girl known as Child K. She's already serving a whole life sentence for the murder of seven babies and the attempted murder of six others.

2885
03:28:33,374 --> 03:28:36,559
[SPEAKER_46]: Sky's chief North of England correspondent Greg Mylam reports.

2886
03:28:38,395 --> 03:28:51,398
[SPEAKER_53]: It is Lucy Letby's status as a multiple murderer and attempted murderer of 13 babies that prosecutors say is an important piece of evidence for the jury in deciding whether she tried to kill a 14th.

2887
03:28:52,280 --> 03:29:03,019
[SPEAKER_53]: Born extremely prematurely, the baby identified as child K had been stable in the neonatal unit at the Countess of Chester Hospital when her condition suddenly worsened.

2888
03:29:04,130 --> 03:29:09,739
[SPEAKER_53]: Consultant Dr Ravi Jayaram walked into the room and found Lucy Letby standing over the baby.

2889
03:29:10,219 --> 03:29:12,483
[SPEAKER_53]: Alarms which should have been going off were not.

2890
03:29:13,044 --> 03:29:14,806
[SPEAKER_53]: Lucy Letby was doing nothing.

2891
03:29:15,207 --> 03:29:19,073
[SPEAKER_53]: The prosecution say the baby's breathing tube had been displaced.

2892
03:29:21,176 --> 03:29:32,213
[SPEAKER_53]: Nick Johnson KC said the fact Lucy Letby was doing nothing and that the alarm was not sounding is evidence that Lucy Letby, the convicted murderer, had displaced the tube.

2893
03:29:33,678 --> 03:29:48,556
[SPEAKER_53]: Mr Johnson told the jury that the baby suffered two further collapses that night, attempts, he said, by Lucy Letby to create the impression, having been caught almost red-handed, that the baby habitually displaced its own breathing tube.

2894
03:29:49,297 --> 03:29:51,400
[SPEAKER_53]: Baby Kay died three days later.

2895
03:29:51,700 --> 03:29:59,550
[SPEAKER_53]: The prosecution say they're not suggesting Lucy Letby's actions caused that death, but they are suggesting that she did try to kill her.

2896
03:30:00,172 --> 03:30:04,898
[SPEAKER_53]: It happened after she'd already murdered five babies and before she murdered two more.

2897
03:30:05,259 --> 03:30:08,663
[SPEAKER_53]: Significant evidence, the prosecution say, of her intention.

2898
03:30:09,705 --> 03:30:17,175
[SPEAKER_53]: Ben Myers, KC, defending Lucy Letby, said she was being blamed wrongly for the death of a baby who was clinically fragile.

2899
03:30:18,176 --> 03:30:23,423
[SPEAKER_53]: A jury was unable to reach a verdict on this allegation at Lucy Letby's previous trial.

2900
03:30:23,904 --> 03:30:25,726
[SPEAKER_53]: She denies attempted murder.

2901
03:30:26,087 --> 03:30:28,710
[SPEAKER_53]: Greg Mylam, Sky News, Manchester Crown Court.

